6. Core Business Rules

BR-SALE-001

Every sold item must exist in inventory.

BR-SALE-002

Sold inventory cannot be sold again.

BR-SALE-003

Invoice number must be unique.

BR-SALE-004

GST calculation automatic.

BR-SALE-005

Inventory deduction automatic.

BR-SALE-006

Sales returns require approval.

BR-SALE-007

Cancelled invoices remain auditable.

BR-SALE-008

All invoices stored permanently.

