8. Pricing Engine

Purpose

Calculate final sale amount.

⸻

Formula

Subtotal:

Subtotal = Metal\ Value + Making\ Charges + Stone\ Charges

⸻

Discounted Amount:

Discounted\ Amount = Subtotal - Discount

⸻

Final Amount:

Final\ Amount = Discounted\ Amount + GST

⸻

9. GST Engine

Purpose

Tax calculation.

⸻

Tax Components

CGST

SGST

IGST

⸻

GST Formula

GST = Taxable\ Amount \times GST\ Rate

⸻

Configuration

GST rates configurable.

⸻

Compliance

GST breakdown mandatory on invoice.

⸻

